openvpn-plugin-auth-script (0.1.0-1+deb9u2) stretch; urgency=medium

  * repackage to be buildable on a pure debian/stable 9 system: use upstream
    Makefile, not meson:
    - debian/control: change Build-Depends: debhelper from >= 11 to >= 10,
      drop meson
    - debian/rules: add "export CFLAGS = -I/usr/include/openvpn", drop
      '--buildsystem=meson' from dh call.
    - debian/install: added

